{"tid":1761126,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港監察：加拿大跨黨派國會議員，支持制裁違反人權香港官員","createTime":"2019-11-28T16:37:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T17:40:26.000Z","uid":278587,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b509af5392eac7850fa73d0dca06a3747c8e47c1","tid":1761126,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T16:37:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/78496191_2497352630385195_1650271102506631168_n_srFe6_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F78496191_2497352630385195_1650271102506631168_n_srFe6_1200x0.png&h=35e7d0a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國民間組織香港監察（Hong Kong Watch）今早透露，超過 60 名加拿大跨黨派國會議員昨日（27日）出席一個有關香港現況的研討會時，大部分國會議員同意動用《馬格尼茨基人權問責法》（Magnitsky law）制裁違反人權的香港官員及警員。<br />\n<br />\n香港監察透過 Facebook 表示，加拿大逾 60 名國會議員周三（27日）出席有關香港現況的活動時，多名保守黨及自由黨眾議員及參議員，均表示支持香港自由民主。席上香港監察受託人Aileen Calverley 建議加拿大動用《馬格尼茨基人權問責法》制裁違反人權的香港官員及警員，大部分出席的議員均在討論環節中表示支持。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯會計師馬格尼茨基（Sergei Magnitsky）因揭發俄羅斯官員貪腐，被當局監禁及以酷刑迫害，2009年死於獄中。美國國會於 2012 年通過《馬格尼茨基人權問責法》以制裁違反人權的俄羅斯官員，英國、加拿大等國亦仿效美國做法制定各自版本的法案。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普周三（28 日）簽署《香港人權與民主法案》，令法案正式生效。香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒今早見記者時表示，眾志於未來 5 年會繼續爭取造成「骨牌效應」，遊說其他國家如加拿大、澳洲、英國、法國、德國等設立類似制裁機制<br />\n<br />\n歐洲議會已於今年 3 月通過決議，敦促歐盟 28 個成員國，各自制定其版本的《馬格尼茨基人權問責法》制裁機制。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/香港監察-加拿大跨黨派國會議員-支持制裁違反人權香港官員/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9B%A3%E5%AF%9F-%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E8%B7%A8%E9%BB%A8%E6%B4%BE%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1-%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E9%81%95%E5%8F%8D%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%AE%98%E5%93%A1%2F&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLZsm%2Bn8Fwo%2F6aJUx9arcu0Q%3D&h=fea1cbd0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9B%A3%E5%AF%9F-%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E8%B7%A8%E9%BB%A8%E6%B4%BE%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1-%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E9%81%95%E5%8F%8D%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%AE%98%E5%93%A1%2F&h=cfad2ca8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/香港監察-加拿大跨黨派國會議員-支持制裁違反人權香港官員/</a>"},{"pid":"d75135ca102fbd23f0b0809a68d6df3d5383cd9b","tid":1761126,"uid":81812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T16:48:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e029081574f883c4d360a1ea8fbb57c384bf012c","tid":1761126,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T17:06:15.000Z","msg":"全球制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f4b6246a1be4fe0d1e8ae419e53bbffe53cfab5","tid":1761126,"uid":322032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e029081574f883c4d360a1ea8fbb57c384bf012c","tid":1761126,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T17:06:15.000Z","msg":"全球制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T17:08:24.000Z","msg":"被鎖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f96ec1ea0b70a35935c1bd7e2c89b243c83bf381","tid":1761126,"uid":256837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T17:40:26.000Z","msg":"唔知共諜Mary Ng會唔會出聲反對呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}